  'The Terminal' game is an airport management game. Land, park, unload, load,
  fuel and take off your fleet. Build and expand your airport with more
  terminal buildings, connect local transportation, enlarge parking facilities
  and more. Buy new airplanes and expand your fleet with new type of jets. The
  better you play the more money you earn, the bigger the terminal became the
  more funds you get to expand your company and fleet.

  On the other hand you always have to pay attention to your fleet. If you do
  not tank them properly you will lose money or even your jets. Moreover, try
  not to crash tankers to planes otherwise you will lose both! Always keep
  clean all your runways from snow, by clicking the snowplows appearing near
  the blue warehouse during snowstorms!
